    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/7f983c43140b45a378c80fab068a3dae.avif?t=1766256154\" width=604 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Office Overloaded is a typing game where you climb up the ranks and improve your typing skills with ever more challenging tasks. Challenge your other co-workers or friends at the global leaderboards to show who is the better typist. Or just play it slow and stay as a stress-free intern at the office.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve your typing skills in a stressful office environment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Type to clear your document tasks for the day, but be fast otherwise you might burn out from the workload and get fired.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/35fbb4436315386c90a894710b4a9514.poster.avif?t=1766256154\" width=606 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/35fbb4436315386c90a894710b4a9514.webm?t=1766256154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/35fbb4436315386c90a894710b4a9514.mp4?t=1766256154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Advance in your ranks as you improve</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Receive more work and different tasks as you get promoted into higher ranks. Start as intern and advance to junior, senior and manager until you can challenge the CEO.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/bcffd21c07abc8e0bcf6d0524f4636f6.poster.avif?t=1766256154\" width=606 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/bcffd21c07abc8e0bcf6d0524f4636f6.webm?t=1766256154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/bcffd21c07abc8e0bcf6d0524f4636f6.mp4?t=1766256154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Purchase items for help</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy a variety of items from the shop to help you at work. A plant to reduce your stress build-up or an assistant to reduce your distractions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/e8e06e5e2cfa945eefcf33086e615444.poster.avif?t=1766256154\" width=606 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/e8e06e5e2cfa945eefcf33086e615444.webm?t=1766256154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/e8e06e5e2cfa945eefcf33086e615444.mp4?t=1766256154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Climb up the global leaderboard</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show your typing skills to the world and become the number one office typist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191960/extras/a2bd239d644e82bc676f64ff1c52b77e.poster.avif?t=1766256154\" width=606 height=202